\"og:description\" content=\"Sayıların sembolik dilini kişisel farkındalık ve içgörü için zarif bir rehbere dönüştüren danışmanlık ve eğitim deneyimleri.\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"tr_TR\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://gonulilhan.com/images/og-gonul-ilhan.png\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"Gönül İlhan Numeroloji Uzmanı\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Gönül İlhan | Numeroloji Uzmanı\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Sayıların sembolik dilini kişisel farkındalık ve içgörü için zarif bir rehbere dönüştüren danışmanlık ve eğitim deneyimleri.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://gonulilhan.com/images/og-gonul-ilhan.png\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image:alt\" content=\"Gönül İlhan Numeroloji Uzmanı\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-screen antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-border/70 bg-ivory/86 backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"container flex h-16 items-center justify-between sm:h-20\"><a class=\"group flex min-w-0 items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3\" aria-label=\"Gönül İlhan ana sayfa\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-gold/40 bg-card text-gold shadow-sm transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-0.5 sm:h-11 sm:w-11\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon-star h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 3a6 6 0 0 0 9 9 9 9 0 1 1-9-9\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"min-w-0 leading-tight\"><span class=\"block truncate font-editorial text-lg text-navy sm:text-xl\">Gönül İlhan</span><span class=\"block truncate text-[0.68rem] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-muted-foreground sm:text-xs sm:tracking-[0.2em]\">Numeroloji</span></span></a><nav class=\"hidden items-center gap-1 lg:flex\" aria-label=\"Ana menü\"><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy\" href=\"/\">Ana Sayfa</a><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy\" href=\"/gonul-ilhan\">Gönül İlhan</a><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy\" href=\"/hizmetler\">Hizmetler</a><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy\" href=\"/egitimler\">Eğitimler</a><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy\" href=\"/yorumlar\">Yorumlar</a><a aria-current=\"page\" class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy bg-card text-navy shadow-sm\" href=\"/yazilar\">Yazılar</a><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition hover:bg-card hover:text-navy\" href=\"/iletisim\">İletişim</a></nav><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-3 lg:flex\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-glow hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-navy/92 min-h-9 px-4 py-2\" href=\"/randevu\">Randevu Al</a></div><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-border bg-card text-navy lg:hidden\" aria-label=\"Menüyü aç\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></header><main><article class=\"container max-w-4xl py-14 sm:py-16\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Kişisel Gelişim</span><h1 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2.55rem] leading-tight text-navy sm:text-6xl\">Sayıların Kişisel Farkındalıktaki Rolü</h1><p class=\"text-base leading-8 text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg sm:leading-9\">Sayılar, kişiliği dar kalıplara hapsetmek yerine davranışlarımızı ve seçimlerimizi gözlemlemek için sembolik ipuçları sunabilir.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-4 w-4 text-gold\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg>27 Nisan 2026</span><span>4 dk<!-- --> okuma</span></div></div><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur mt-10\"><div class=\"min-w-0 p-5 sm:p-10\"><div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\"><p class=\"mb-6 text-base leading-8 text-muted-foreground sm:leading-9\">Kişisel farkındalık, çoğu zaman kendimize dışarıdan bakabilme becerisiyle başlar. Numerolojide sayılar, bu bakışı kolaylaştıran sembolik başlıklar sunar: başlangıç, denge, ifade, düzen, özgürlük, sorumluluk, içgörü, güç ve tamamlama gibi.</p><p class=\"mb-6 text-base leading-8 text-muted-foreground sm:leading-9\">Bu başlıklar kişinin hayatındaki gerçek deneyimlerle birleştiğinde anlam kazanır. Bir sayı tek başına kişiyi tanımlamaz; ancak belirli davranış örüntülerini, ihtiyaçları ve gelişim alanlarını fark etmek için nazik bir dil sağlayabilir.</p><p class=\"mb-6 text-base leading-8 text-muted-foreground sm:leading-9\">Bu nedenle numeroloji çalışması, kişinin kendine daha şefkatli ve dürüst bakmasına yardımcı olduğunda değerlidir. Amaç kontrol etmek değil, anlamak ve daha bilinçli seçimler yapabilmektir.</p></div><div class=\"mt-8 rounded-2xl border border-gold/25 bg-gold-sheen p-5\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Bu içerik kişisel farkındalık ve ilham amaçlıdır; tıbbi, psikolojik, hukuki veya finansal danışmanlık yerine geçmez.</p></div><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-glow hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-navy/92 min-h-11 px-6 py-2\" href=\"/randevu\">Seans İçin Randevu Al</a><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border border-border bg-card/70 text-foreground hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 hover:bg-card min-h-11 px-6 py-2\" href=\"/egitimler\">Eğitimleri Gör<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></article><section class=\"container space-y-8 pb-16\"><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] text-navy sm:text-4xl\">İlgili yazılar</h2><div class=\"grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group h-full transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-gold/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 flex h-full flex-col gap-5 p-5 sm:p-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Numeroloji Temelleri</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-3.5 w-3.5\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg>12 Mayıs 2026</span><span class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">4 dk</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\"><a class=\"hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/numeroloji-nedir\">Numeroloji Nedir?</a></h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Numerolojiyi kehanet değil, sayıların sembolik dili üzerinden kişisel farkındalık geliştiren bir bakış açısı olarak ele alalım.</p></div><a class=\"mt-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-navy transition hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/numeroloji-nedir\">Yazıyı Oku<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group h-full transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-gold/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 flex h-full flex-col gap-5 p-5 sm:p-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Döngüler</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-3.5 w-3.5\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg>8 Mayıs 2026</span><span class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">5 dk</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\"><a class=\"hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/kisisel-yil-dongusu-ne-anlama-gelir\">Kişisel Yıl Döngüsü Ne Anlama Gelir?</a></h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Her yılın farklı bir teması olabilir. Kişisel yıl döngüsü, içinde bulunduğun döneme daha bilinçli bakmana yardımcı olur.</p></div><a class=\"mt-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-navy transition hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/kisisel-yil-dongusu-ne-anlama-gelir\">Yazıyı Oku<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"min-w-0 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/82 text-card-foreground shadow-soft backdrop-blur group h-full transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-gold/45\"><div class=\"min-w-0 flex h-full flex-col gap-5 p-5 sm:p-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center whitespace-normal rounded-full border border-gold/30 bg-champagne/18 px-3 py-1 text-center text-xs font-medium leading-snug text-navy\">Eğitim</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-3.5 w-3.5\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg>2 Mayıs 2026</span><span class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">3 dk</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><h3 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-2xl leading-tight text-navy\"><a class=\"hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/numeroloji-egitimine-kimler-katilabilir\">Numeroloji Eğitimine Kimler Katılabilir?</a></h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground\">Numeroloji eğitimi yalnızca danışman olmak isteyenler için değil, kendini tanıma yolculuğunu derinleştirmek isteyen herkes için uygun olabilir.</p></div><a class=\"mt-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-navy transition hover:text-gold\" href=\"/yazilar/numeroloji-egitimine-kimler-katilabilir\">Yazıyı Oku<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"container py-14 sm:py-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"sacred-frame overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-navy-depth p-5 text-primary-foreground shadow-soft min-[390px]:p-6 sm:p-12 lg:p-14\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] lg:items-center\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-champagne sm:text-sm sm:tracking-[0.24em]\">Nazik bir başlangıç</p><h2 class=\"break-words font-editorial text-[2rem] leading-tight sm:text-5xl\">Kendi yolculuğunu sayılarla keşfetmeye hazır mısın?</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-8 text-primary-foreground/76\">Bir seans, eğitim ya da atölye ile numerolojiyi hayatına sakin, etik ve ilham veren bir farkındalık alanı olarak davet edebilirsin.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row lg:flex-col\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center font-medium transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 shadow-glow hover:-translate-y-0.5 min-h-12 px-7 py-3 text-base w-full bg-champagne text-navy hover:bg-linen sm:w-auto lg:w-full\" href=\"/randevu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg>Randevu Al</a><a class=\"inline-flex min-w-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-normal rounded-full text-center font-medium transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;&gt;svg]:shrink-0 border hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-gold/50 min-h-12 px-7 py-3 text-base w-full border-white/20 bg-white/8 text-primary-foreground hover:bg-white/14 sm:w-auto lg:w-full\" href=\"/egitimler\">Eğitimleri İncele<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-border/70 bg-navy text-primary-foreground\"><div class=\"container grid gap-9 py-12 sm:gap-10 sm:py-14 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr_0.8fr]\"><div class=\"max-w-md space-y-5\"><div class=\"flex min-w-0 items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-champagne/40 text-champagne\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon-star h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 3a6 6 0 0 0 9 9 9 9 0 1 1-9-9\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path></svg></span><div><p class=\"font-editorial text-2xl\">Gönül İlhan</p><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-champagne/80 sm:tracking-[0.22em]\">Numeroloji Uzmanı</p></div></div><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-primary-foreground/76\">Sayıların sembolik dilini kişisel farkındalık, içgörü ve daha bilinçli seçimler için zarif bir rehbere dönüştüren danışmanlık ve eğitim alanı.</p><p class=\"rounded-2xl border border-champagne/20 bg-white/5 p-4 text-xs leading-6 text-primary-foreground/70\">Numeroloji içerikleri kişisel farkındalık ve ilham amaçlıdır; tıbbi, psikolojik, hukuki veya finansal danışmanlık yerine geçmez.</p></div><div><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-champagne\">Menü</h2><ul class=\"space-y-3 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"text-primary-foreground/76 transition hover:text-champagne\" href=\"/\">Ana 